code: /* inspo from this site https://krazydad.com/tutorials/makecolors.php */export var lineColorGenerator=function lineColorGenerator(i,lenght){var phase=arguments.length>2&&arguments[2]!==undefined?arguments[2]:0;var center=128;var width=127;var frequency=Math.PI*2/lenght;var red=Math.round(Math.sin(frequency*i+2+phase)*width+center);var green=Math.round(Math.sin(frequency*i+0+phase)*width+center);var blue=Math.round(Math.sin(frequency*i+4+phase)*width+center);return[red,green,blue];};
